summary: My preset for Brooke Wylde for Racemenu. This mod is dedicated to her.
descriptionHtml:
This is my preset for Brooke Wylde, the adult film star. This mod is highly dedicated to her and her fans. You can now play as her in Skyrim.

How to install: Put the file in "Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets(if folders do not exist, create them, I think Racemenu has them)", either start a new game or type in showracemenu in the console, naviagate to "presets", press F9 to load preset and select the file.

Race: Breton

Required Mods:

ApachiiSkyHair
Kawaii Face Presets
CBBE
Mikan Eyes
RANs Headmesh(type B)
RaceMenu and Racemenu plugin
SKSE

Not required but recommended:
Bodyslide
Immersive Armors
Daedric Sword Redux
All Geared Up
JRC's Witcher Style Sword Pack
Crash Fixes
HDT Physics
SkyUI
A Matter of Time
XPMS and/or XPMS Extended
Not Another Colored Map Icon Mod - NACMIM
Not Another Colored Map Icon Mod - SkyUI 5.1 Patch

Weapons and armor used in screenshots:
JRC's Witcher Style Sword Pack
Daedric Sword Redux
Ancient Nord Chainmail CBBE HDT


Again, be sure to pick your race as a breton for best results before loading the preset.
author: LordMala
